snippet.title: Rise of the Ronin - Release Date Trailer | Game Awards 2023
snippet.description:
Embark on an epic journey across war-torn 19th-century Japan in this combat-focused open-world action RPG from Team Ninja. Rise of the Ronin is coming March 22, 2024 on PlayStation 5.
